Bosse_Agdistis_Status_Down For The Count: Unable to move or execute actions.
ContentDesc_Abyssos - Siebter Kreis: Erichthonios's mind falls into the hands of the enemy, and he is spirited away to Tartaros, Pandæmonium's deepest circle. The only path to his rescue goes through Agdistis, whose magicks are peerless among the keywards─even more so now that they have been augmented by Hephaistos's endless experimentation. To deliver her soul from suffering and bring Erichthonios to safety, you must face your most daunting foe yet.
Instancecontenttextdata_34601_Text: Is this what became of the keyward? How dreadful...
Instancecontenttextdata_34602_Text: She means to send you plummeting into the abyss. Allow me to soften your landing.
Instancecontenttextdata_34603_Text: Perhaps you require more room for heroics.
Instancecontenttextdata_34604_Text: Leave me to my research, or be...become...
Instancecontenttextdata_34605_Text: I shall give you ground on which to fight, but you must move deftly!
Instancecontenttextdata_34606_Text: She knows only destruction... I shall do my best to keep up with her rage!
Instancecontenttextdata_34613_Text: Begone from my sight or suffer...SUFFER!
Instancecontenttextdata_34614_Text: I sense convergences of aether... Beware what they may spawn!
Instancecontenttextdata_34615_Text: If you will not leave... Then YOU shall become MINE!
Instancecontenttextdata_34616_Text: I am...Agdistis? Yes...and this is my vessel. Have I been gifted new test subjects?
